** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player has not taken the wine jugs and has inventory space:}}
** {{tbox|You help yourself to rewards from the table. You can now retrieve these from Diango, or from Party Pete for the duration of this event. The Old School team wishes you a Happy 12th Birthday!}}
