==Talking to Deviled Dave==
* '''Deviled Dave:''' Om nom nom.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|Are you just scoffing all of the deviled eggs?}}
** '''Player:''' Are you just scoffing all of the deviled eggs?
** '''Deviled Dave:''' Mmmfmfmm! No? Just the tasty ones. Look, they're my favourite and I don't get to eat them very often.
** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|Who are you?}}
** '''Player:''' Who are you?
** '''Deviled Dave:''' I'm Deviled Dave, finisher of deviled eggs, demolisher of balloons and the most EVIL party guest.
** '''Player:''' Wait a second. Dave? Evil Dave?
** '''Deviled Dave:''' Shhhhhh! I'm in disguise! In EVIL disguise.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' Not a demon-summoning level of evil disguise, just a normal, garden-variety level of evil disguise.
** '''Player:''' What in the world are you doing here?
** '''Deviled Dave:''' Eating Party Pete's famous deviled eggs of course! They're my favourite other than spicy stew. I overheard my mo- mate talking with Ger- a friend about a birthday party with deviled eggs.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' They mentioned costumes too, so I thought I'd crash the party by putting on my most EVIL costume, because I want to be in disguise, but still EVIL.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' I even changed my name. I was sure nobody would recognize me.
** '''Player:''' You almost had me fooled.
** {{tcond|If the player has already unlocked the rewards:}}
*** {{tact|other}}
** '''Deviled Dave:''' I think Party Pete's onto me too and is going to stop me enjoying the nibbles soon because I stand out like a hellcat. I need to blend in so he won't be suspicious.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' I know, how about I give YOU a costume. Then you can also be EVIL and I won't stand out so much! Yes! Perfect!
** {{tcond|If the player has less than three inventory slots:}}
*** {{tbox|You need [{{colour|#ff0000|x}}] free inventory slots to receive your Birthday event rewards.}}
*** {{tact|other}}
** {{tcond|If the player has three inventory slots:}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Classic imp hood detail.png|pic2=Classic imp tail detail.png|Deviled Dave gives you a Classic Imp costume!}}
*** '''Deviled Dave:''' By the way, earlier I grabbed all of that free stuff from the table over there. There was a message with it: The Old School team wishes you a Happy 12th Birthday!
*** '''Deviled Dave:''' I'll let Diango know you can have it too, because then you can reclaim any of it from Party Pete and distract him further!
*** '''Deviled Dave:''' My plan is flawless! Ah-ha-ha-ha-ha-haa!
*** {{tact|other}}
* {{topt|What kind of costume are you wearing?}}
** '''Player:''' What kind of costume are you wearing?
** '''Deviled Dave:''' You know imps, right? Evil little critters. Tried to summon them once. Well, when I was little, in my bedtime story books, they were little guys wearing an outfit just like this one! Well, except for the legs.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' I just wasn't ready to commit to red trousers just for a costume. I'm more of a robes kind of man, like these Zamorak monk robes. I like the freedom. Just don't ask where I got them.
** '''Deviled Dave:''' But yeah, it's been my go-to costume for parties for years. Not that I get invited to many parties. After all I'm just too EVIL!
** {{tact|other}}

